QuestData.Title: Breathing Room
QuestData.Description: Our forces are not ready to assault Astranaar just yet, $c. They know we're coming, though, and they're not content to sit and wait for us. At the base of this cliff they've created a camp from which they launch bothersome attacks by the light of the moon.$b$bBefore these skirmishes bolster their confidence any further, I want you to visit them with the wrath of the Horde! Return to me when the elves have been humbled a bit.
QuestData.LogDescription: Captain Goggath wants you to kill 10 Astranaar Skirmishers and 3 Astranaar Officers.
QuestData.CompletionText: Well, $r, have you taught the elves a little humility?
QuestData.RewardText: Well done, $r. But there is much that remains to be done here.
